Package: leafcirclelegend
Title: Add a Scaled Circle Legend to a Leaflet Map
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "Campbell", , "paul.campbell@epicentre.msf.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1018-6606"))
Description: The leaflet R package does not have legend option for circle markers scaled to a vector of data.
  This package provides a single function to rectify this problem.
